attributes.background:
Such disabilities and health issues can be:

• being deaf or hearing impaired;

• suffering from aphasia;

• having cognitive problems which make concentrating on and remembering spoken language difficult;

• being easily fatigued by attempts to maintain a conversation or direct interaction with another person;

• having difficulty with hand-use for writing down verbal information provided over the phone. This can be due to either physical or cognitive problems or a combination of both;

• having a speech impediment;

• having a phobia of speaking on the telephone;

amongst many other health problems which can cause false indications of the claimants honesty.
